column5: Good luck to all, I'm leaving for the Bay in a few hours, and hoping for some luck on the back of Wednesday's full moon, and a report as well! Who else is fishing this weekend; where are you headed? Backbay

you can count me in ~ I got a head start last night and slayed the perch... final tally was 61 kept and at least 3 times that thrown back ! All sizes kept were above 10" .  I plan on hitting the water tomorrow and sunday ! Bassin all the way !
Going to Windmill Point in Fort Erie on Saturday, then heading somewhere with a fellow OFC'er on Sunday! Hopefully I'll catch something and make another report! lol
